Canada to Pull Out of Kyoto Protocol Next Month, CTV News Says

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 
2011-11-28T10:22:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-28/canada-to-pull-out-of-kyoto-protocol-next-month-ctv-news-says.html
Canada will announce next month that
it will withdraw from the  Kyoto Protocol ,  CTV News reported ,
without saying how it obtained the information.  The Canadian government has tentatively planned an
announcement for a few days before Christmas, according to the
CTV News website. The report comes as nations gathered in
Durban,  South Africa  to discuss a global climate agreement for
the period after 2012.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
 m.carr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  